      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014truly like-new and handled with so much love. I\u2019ve kept it sparkling inside and out, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with its next lucky owner today. It drives like a dream and looks even better. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
