    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine example of the E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This unit has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including VAC Motorsports rod bearings and a Beisan Systems VANOS overhaul. The chassis is structurally sound with a reinforced rear subframe. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M-differential. The suspension retains its factory-tuned damping with zero bushing deflection, ensuring surgical turn-in. Truly a turn-key collector-grade machine for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
