    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I am honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in such pristine condition that it basically still has that new-car smell! It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dings, just pure perfection. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
